from itertools import permutations
MOD = 10 ** 9 - 7

def calculate_sum_of_permutations(digits):
    str_digits = [str(digit) for digit in digits]
    total_sum = 0
    for perm in permutations(str_digits):
        number = int(''.join(perm))
        total_sum += number
    return total_sum % MOD
